DATABASE DESIGN


1.	Entity Name:  Aircraft

Attributes	Type
AircraftID	          int
Model	          varchar(50)
Capacity	int
Manufacturer	varchar(50)
YearOfManufacture	int


2.	Entity Name:  Seat

Attributes	Type
SeatId	int
      AircraftId	varchar(5)
  SeatNumber	varchar(20)
Availability	bit


3.	Entity Name:  Airline

Attributes	Type
AirlineID	int
Name	varchar(50)
          Country 	varchar(50)
IATA_CODE	varchar(5)
ICAO_CODE	varchar(5)


4.	Entity Name:  Passenger

Attributes	Type
PassengerId	Int
          Name	Varchar(50)
DOB	Date
PassportNumber	Varchar(20)
Nationality	Varchar(50)


5.	Entity Name:  Flight

Attributes	Type
FlightID	int
AirlineID	Int
AircraftID	Int
Source	varchar(50)
Destination	varchar(50)
DepartureTime	Datetime
ArrivalTime	Datetime
Status	Varchar(20)



6.	Entity Name:  Payment

Attributes	Type
PaymentID	int
PassengerID	int
Amount	Decimal(10,2)
PaymentMethod	varchar(20)
PaymentDate	Date
	

7.	Entity Name:  Ticket

Attributes	Type
TicketID	int(10)
PassengerID	int(10)
FlightID	int(10)
SeatID	int(10)
Class	Varchar(20)
Price	Decimal(10,2)
	

8.	Entity Name:  Booking

Attributes	Type
BookingID	int
PassengerID	Int
FlightId	Int
BookingDate	Date 
Status	varchar(20)


9.	Entity Name:  Crew

Attributes	Type
CrewId	int(10)
Name	Varchar(50)
Role	Varchar(30)
FlightID	int

10.	Entity Name:  baggage

Attributes	Type
BaggageID	Int
passengerID	Int
Weight	Decimal(5,2)
TagNumber	           Varchar(20)
Status	varchar(20)
FlightID	int


11.	Entity Name:  CheckIn

Attributes	Type
CheckInID	int
passengerID	Int
FlightID	Int
SeatNumber	Varchar(5)
CheckInTime	DateTime


12.	Entity Name:  Meal

Attributes	Type
MealID	int
PassengerID	Int
FlightID	int
MealType	varchar(20)
SpecialRequest	Varchar(50)
13.Entity Name: SecurityCheck

Attributes	Type
SecurityID	Int
PassengerID	Int
FlightID	Int
Status	Varchar(20)
TimeChecked	DateTime

14.	Entity Name: BoardingPass

Attributes	Type
BoardingPassID	Int
PassengerID	Int
FlightID	Int
GateNumber	Varchar(5)
BoardingTime	DateTime

15.	Entity Name: FlightSchedule

Attributes	Type
FlightID	Int
Airline	Varchar(50)
DepartureCity	Varchar(50)
ArrivalCity	Varchar(50)
DepartureTime	DateTime
ArrivalTime	DateTime
